  <summary date="2021-03-10T17:58:11Z" status="Public Law">Crisis Stabilization and Community Reentry Act of 2020

This bill authorizes the Department of Justice to award grants for states, Native American tribes, local governments, and community-based nonprofit organizations to provide clinical services for people with serious mental illness and substance use disorders who need mental health services upon release from a correctional facility.</summary>
